      LARGO ROOF REPAIR<br/><span class="gt">EMERGENCY LEAK REPAIR</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Happy Roof provides fast, reliable roof repair in Largo, Pinellas County's largest city. From emergency leak response to storm damage repair, our licensed crews deliver honest assessments and quality workmanship across every Largo neighborhood.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-t">Get a Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INFO STRIP -->
<div style="background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;padding:.85rem 0">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Largo, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Choose Happy Roof for Repairs</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY LARGO HOMEOWNERS TRUST US FOR ROOF REPAIRS</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Largo's central location on the Pinellas peninsula means it catches weather from both sides - Gulf storms from the west and Tampa Bay squalls from the east. Summer thunderstorms dump inches of rain in minutes, testing every weak point on a roof. When your Largo home develops a leak after a downpour, or a tropical storm tears shingles off your roof near Largo Central Park, you need a contractor who responds fast and fixes the problem right.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">The most common repairs we perform in Largo are replacing wind-damaged shingles on the 1960s and 1970s ranch homes near Belcher Road and Indian Rocks Road, resealing pipe boots and flashing on mid-century homes throughout the city, and addressing water intrusion issues in the townhome communities near Bardmoor and Imperial Point. Many of Largo's older homes have roofs with original or deteriorated rubber pipe boots that crack in the Florida sun, creating slow leaks that can go unnoticed for months.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Happy Roof gives honest advice on every Largo repair. If your roof can be effectively repaired, that is what we recommend. If we find damage that makes replacement the better long-term investment, we explain why clearly. For emergency leaks, we offer same-day tarping. See our <a href="/largo-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Largo roofing page</a> or our <a href="/roof-repair" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">roof repair page</a> for more details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Emergency Leak Response</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Same-day emergency tarping for active leaks in Largo. We contain the water intrusion immediately, then schedule a permanent repair.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Storm & Wind Damage</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Largo catches Gulf and Bay storms alike. We repair all wind and water damage and help document everything for your insurance claim.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Pipe Boot & Flashing Repair</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">The most common roof repair in Largo. Cracked rubber pipe boots and deteriorated flashing around vents and chimneys cause most residential leaks.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Honest Recommendations</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">If a repair will protect your Largo home, we recommend a repair. If replacement makes more sense, we tell you straight. No upselling, no games.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED / COMMON REPAIRS / WHAT WE CHECK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
