        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Shingle Wind Damage</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Largo's exposure to Gulf and Bay winds means shingles get lifted, cracked, and torn regularly. We match your existing shingles and replace damaged sections.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
